    "summary": "Thirty-four women law graduates completed a five-month legal empowerment internship in Mogadishu, the first cohort under a government initiative to address gender disparities in Somalia's justice sector.",
    "content": "Mogadishu — On July 22, 2026, thirty-four women law graduates officially completed a five-month national legal empowerment internship, marking the end of the first cohort under a broader government initiative that will run until May 2027. The program, based in Mogadishu, was designed to address long-standing gender imbalances within Somalia's justice system by creating a pathway for women to work in courts, prosecution offices, and the Ministry of Justice and Constitutional Affairs.\n\nThe initiative is part of a larger effort by the Federal Government of Somalia, in collaboration with international partners, to strengthen the rule of law and ensure greater representation of women in legal institutions. The graduates received practical training in legal procedures, case management, and court operations, equipping them with skills to serve as prosecutors, judges, and legal advisors.\n\nKey figures involved in the program include officials from the Somali Ministry of Justice and Constitutional Affairs, as well as representatives from the United Nations, the European Union, and the Netherlands, who provided financial and technical support. The project also involves state-level judicial institutions, ensuring a coordinated approach across federal and regional authorities.\n\nFor the Somali diaspora, this development highlights progress in gender equality and institutional reform in Somalia. It signals a shift toward more inclusive governance and could inspire similar initiatives in diaspora communities. The graduates are expected to return to their regions to work in legal roles, contributing to a more equitable justice system.\n\nRead the original report from Radio Dalsan here: https://radiodalsan.com/2026/07/22/somalia-completes-first-legal-internship-for-34-women-lawyers/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=somalia-completes-first-legal-internship-for-34-women-lawyers",
